Kerala
Sep 17, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			The police have arrested the father of a girl at Kottakkal and her madrassa teacher for allegedly raping her. A search is on for one more person who allegedly abused her. The girl, a sixth standard student, told the police that her madrassa teacher abused her sexually on September 11. She also testified against her father and a neighbour in connection with sexual abuse.